&lt;p class=&quot;ql-align-justify&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;ABOUT MOBSQUAD&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;ql-align-justify&quot; style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;We are a well-funded, hyper-growth, company looking for an experienced Machine Learning Engineer.&amp;nbsp; If you’ve ever dreamed of working with a top tier technology company backed by the very best venture capitalists in the world, then this is your chance.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
